# Project Tooling Override

This library uses **spago.yaml** (not spago.dhall). Build: `spago build`.

Use `npm run format` and `purs-tidy` where applicable; add these scripts if missing.

No AppM; this is a component/utility library. Re-export barrels under `Halogen.DaisyUI.*`.
